</div>
<div>
<p>　　太祖<date notBefore="963" notAfter="968">乾德</date>元年<pc>，</pc>始有事於南郊<pc>。</pc>自<date notBefore="9999" notAfter="9999">
<num value="5">五</num>代</date>以來<pc>，</pc>喪亂相繼<pc>，</pc>典章制度<pc>，</pc>多所散逸<pc>。</pc>至是<pc>，</pc>詔有司講求遺逸<pc>，</pc>遵行典故<pc>，</pc>以副寅恭之意<pc>。</pc>是歲<measure quantity="11" unit="months">
<num value="11">十一</num>月</measure>
<measure quantity="16" unit="days">
<num value="16">十六</num>日</measure>
<pc>，</pc>合祭天地於圜丘<pc>。</pc>初<pc>，</pc>有司議配享<pc>，</pc>請以僖祖升配<pc>，</pc>張昭獻議曰<pc>：</pc>
